Toshiyuki Nishida was nominated for the Best Actor award at the 2004 Japanese Academy Awards for his performance as the head of a yakuza clan.
The Japanese title  'Geroppa!'  is the Japanese transliteration of the lyric "Get up!" from the James Brown song "Get Up (I Feel Like Being A) Sex Machine".
The cast includes Toshiyuki Nishida (Hanemura, the Yakuza boss), Takako Tokiwa (Kaori), Taro Yamamoto (Taro), Ittoku Kishibe (Kaneyama), Kenta Kiritani (Haruhiko), Kohei Yoshida (Kenji), Keiji Nagatsuka (Okabe), Willie Raynor (James Brown impersonator) and Adeyto (Marilyn Monroe impersonator).
